    Blazorise Offcanvas component
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Offcanvas is a component that provides a flexible way to display content off-canvas, such as menus, sidebars, or additional information.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    The Offcanvas component consists of the main container, OffcanvasContent, and several slots for content, including OffcanvasHeader, OffcanvasBody, and OffcanvasFooter.
</DocsPageParagraph>

